{"name":"46b8720d695c928acffa","layouts":[{"id":0,"position":{"x":16,"y":16,"z":1001,"width":1264.0000000000002,"height":704,"tabOrder":1001}}],"singleVisual":{"visualType":"scriptVisual","projections":{"Values":[{"queryRef":"Characters.Character"},{"queryRef":"Characters.Path"},{"queryRef":"Characters.Element"},{"queryRef":"Characters.Rarity"}]},"prototypeQuery":{"Version":2,"From":[{"Name":"c","Entity":"Characters","Type":0}],"Select":[{"Column":{"Expression":{"SourceRef":{"Source":"c"}},"Property":"Character"},"Name":"Characters.Character","NativeReferenceName":"Character"},{"Column":{"Expression":{"SourceRef":{"Source":"c"}},"Property":"Path"},"Name":"Characters.Path","NativeReferenceName":"Path"},{"Column":{"Expression":{"SourceRef":{"Source":"c"}},"Property":"Element"},"Name":"Characters.Element","NativeReferenceName":"Element"},{"Column":{"Expression":{"SourceRef":{"Source":"c"}},"Property":"Rarity"},"Name":"Characters.Rarity","NativeReferenceName":"Rarity"}],"OrderBy":[{"Direction":1,"Expression":{"Column":{"Expression":{"SourceRef":{"Source":"c"}},"Property":"Character"}}}]},"drillFilterOtherVisuals":true,"hasDefaultSort":true,"objects":{"script":[{"properties":{"source":{"expr":{"Literal":{"Value":"'# The following code to create a dataframe and remove duplicated rows is always executed and acts as a preamble for your script:

library(ggplot2)
library(patchwork)
library(treemapify)
dataset$Rarity <- factor(dataset$Rarity, levels = c(''5'', ''4''))
# Calculate the count of characters for each rarity category
rarity_counts <- table(dataset$Rarity)

# Convert the result to a data frame
rarity_counts_df <- as.data.frame(rarity_counts)
names(rarity_counts_df) <- c("Rarity", "count")

# Calculate the count of characters for each rarity and path combination
rarity_path_counts <- table(dataset$Rarity, dataset$Path, dataset$Element)

# Convert the result to a data frame
rarity_path_counts_df <- as.data.frame(rarity_path_counts)

# Rename the columns
names(rarity_path_counts_df) <- c("Rarity","Path", "Element", "Count")

custom_palette <- c("Lightning" = "darkorchid4",
                    "Physical" = "lavenderblush4",
                    "Quantum" = "slateblue4",
                    "Wind" = "chartreuse2",
                    "Imaginary" = "gold2",
                    "Fire" = "brown1",
                    "Ice" = "cadetblue1")

custom_xtick_colors <- c("Abundance" = "gold2",
                    "Destruction" = "brown",
                    "Erudition" = "red",
                    "Harmony" = "green",
                    "Hunt" = "limegreen",
                    "Nihility" = "purple",
                    "Preservation" = "cyan")

custom_palette_r <- c(''5'' = "gold", ''4'' = "purple")
  
p1 <- ggplot(rarity_path_counts_df, aes(area = Count, fill = Path, label = Element, subgroup = Rarity, subgroup2 = Path)) +
  geom_treemap(color = "#8B8B83", size = 1) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = custom_xtick_colors) + 
  geom_treemap_subgroup_text(place = "centre", grow = TRUE,
                             alpha = 0.25, color = "black",
                             fontface = "italic") +
  geom_treemap_text(color = "white", place = "centre",
                    size = 5, grow = TRUE) +
  geom_treemap_subgroup_border(colour = "#FFFFF0", size = 5) +
  geom_treemap_subgroup2_border(colour = "#EEEEE0", size = 2) +
  ggtitle("Rarity, Path, and Element Distribution") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 15, hjust = 0.5)) 

p2 <- ggplot(dataset, aes(x = Rarity, fill = Rarity)) +
  geom_bar() +
  scale_fill_manual(values = custom_palette_r) +
  geom_text(aes(label = ..count..), stat = "count", vjust = -1, colour = "black") +
  labs(y = "Count of Characters") + ylim(c(0, 30))

p3 <- ggplot(dataset, aes(x = Path, fill = Path)) +
  geom_bar() +
  scale_fill_manual(values = custom_xtick_colors) +
  geom_text(aes(label = ..count..), stat = "count", vjust = -1, colour = "black") +
  labs(y = "Count of Characters") + ylim(c(0, 10))

p4 <- ggplot(dataset, aes(x = Element, fill = Element)) +
  geom_bar() +
  scale_fill_manual(values = custom_palette) +
  geom_text(aes(label = ..count..), stat = "count", vjust = -1, colour = "black") +
  labs(y = "Count of Characters") + ylim(c(0, 10))

p1 + (p2 / p3 / p4)'"}}},"provider":{"expr":{"Literal":{"Value":"'R'"}}}}}]},"vcObjects":{"title":[{"properties":{"text":{"expr":{"Literal":{"Value":"''"}}}}}]}}}
